{"tid":1068020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"摸熟睡女兒下體　大家是否接受瘦父解釋?","createTime":"2019-03-19T02:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T03:55:09.000Z","uid":72009,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4206c5e3bc60f0d22b0c6e969f97da1f2a8f8bcd","tid":1068020,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:49:46.000Z","msg":"台北市一名父親被控撫摸國中女兒的下體，他辯稱因女兒曾經被人性侵，才仿效日本性教育，教女兒不要因而瞧不起自己。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，台北地檢署指控，57歲父親在2009年9月到2011年6月間的某晚，乘女兒熟睡之際，隔著內褲撫摸女兒下體，女兒向學校心理諮商中心求援，校方通報警察介入查辦，檢警約談父親。<br />\n<br />\n父親供稱，因女兒曾被陌生男子猥褻，他才仿效日本性教育的方式，摸女兒下體是要教導她知道自己是被強迫的，不要因而看不起自己，檢方依乘機猥褻罪嫌起訴。台北地院昨依成年人故意對少年犯乘機猥褻罪判他有期徒刑1年，緩刑5年。可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190319/1535756/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190319%2F1535756%2F&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=642c7abd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190319%2F1535756%2F&h=9b7c33f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190319/1535756/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原因"},{"pid":"79baab6c5ed866dd75d9c8d580dedd50b40cd21c","tid":1068020,"uid":202370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:30:50.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d471a3691791e97e6b742c0d5d347d7a98e13c50","tid":1068020,"uid":129821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"估中係台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc88639a779c77b9730e41989a49b699bd28a5f","tid":1068020,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d471a3691791e97e6b742c0d5d347d7a98e13c50","tid":1068020,"uid":129821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"